        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer373205827" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13897101790468936465">I decided to read this because &apos;The Heart is a Lonely Hunter&quot; and &quot;The Member of the Wedding&quot; are two of my favourite novels. The Ballad of the Sad Cafe is similar in several ways (desolate Southern nowhere-town, achingly lonely misfits as main characters, shockingly sad ending). I&apos;ve given this only three stars though because the story is undermined a little by some clunky narration e.g. &quot;So compose from such flashes an image of these years as a whole. And for a moment let it rest&quot;. </span>
  <span id="freeText13897101790468936465" style="display:none">I decided to read this because 'The Heart is a Lonely Hunter" and "The Member of the Wedding" are two of my favourite novels. The Ballad of the Sad Cafe is similar in several ways (desolate Southern nowhere-town, achingly lonely misfits as main characters, shockingly sad ending). I've given this only three stars though because the story is undermined a little by some clunky narration e.g. "So compose from such flashes an image of these years as a whole. And for a moment let it rest". </span>
  <a data-text-id="13897101790468936465" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

