          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/814524-yourfiendmrjones?shelf=the-drama-rama">the-drama-rama</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/814524-yourfiendmrjones?shelf=litra-char">litra-char</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1966859993" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10318152889422744811">The play, like the original story, has the weird Southern patois to sift through, making it a challenge to stay fully engaged.<br/><br/>Having said that, the final 2-3 pages are some of the most poetically beautiful narration I&apos;ve ever read.</span>
  <span id="freeText10318152889422744811" style="display:none">The play, like the original story, has the weird Southern patois to sift through, making it a challenge to stay fully engaged.<br /><br />Having said that, the final 2-3 pages are some of the most poetically beautiful narration I've ever read.</span>
  <a data-text-id="10318152889422744811" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


